https://twitter.com/jackabryan/status/1497634221468229633?s=21</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Iu0iDxH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ridiculousbudget]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Been thinking about the narrative</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Ks86b3f</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sTowjg0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Don't see shaming of surrendered soldier happen often here, but see it enough online. Pushing the first narrative has the benefit of possibly bolstering Ukrainian moral, but the downside would be Russia viewing its relative restraint in use of force as weak. What Russia has done so far is an atrocity, but it is far less than what they could be doing.

The upside of the second narrative is hopefully persuading Russian invaders to surrender rather than fight this needless war. This would help negate the following potential play.

I worry the first wave of Russian invaders was made up of the less devoted and nationalistic units. Why do this? 1) Thin the ranks of the loyally weakest and 2) Show the growing Russian casualty list to the more fanatical 2nd wave troops to justify upcoming atrocities. This is purely speculation on my part.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Ks86b3f</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kaiserkevin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>real leaders</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NEE4VtS</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e7gjs9R.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NEE4VtS</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SkyNetIsInevitable]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>when the tattoo doesn't mean what you think it does</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9gGoBLa</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5UhZdr8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QvsTS6E.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/piBfniL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6BkAZFS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/58A0JBI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V9uLRFX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YaU18FH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yqtPbiB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5Uu6M0W.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></